  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "To make the conversation more natural, psychotherapists provide a set of questions they typically ask in each dimension (7 to 11 sample questions).",
    "We prompt a GPT-4-based Rephraser [66] to rephrase these questions (structurally instead of semantically) when asking questions.Each dimension has one related question.",
    "The Q-learning agent has 39 states (37 questions, start, and end).",
    "We set the learning rate and discount factor to 0.1 and 0.9, respectively.",
    "The probability of selecting the best action is set as 𝜖 = 0.9.The therapists determine the initial Q-values for the Q-table based on their empirical evaluation of the \"importance\" of the dimensions."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "We prompt a GPT-4-based Rephraser [66] to rephrase these questions (structurally instead of semantically) when asking questions.Each dimension has one related question."
  ]
